      • query

        public CatalogitemCursor query(android.content.ContentResolver contentResolver,
                               String[] projection,
                               String sortOrder)
        Query the given content resolver using this selection.
        Parameters:
        contentResolver - The content resolver to query.
        projection - A list of which columns to return. Passing null will return all columns, which is inefficient.
        sortOrder - How to order the rows, formatted as an SQL ORDER BY clause (excluding the ORDER BY itself). Passing null will use the default sort order, which may be unordered.
        Returns:
        A CatalogitemCursor object, which is positioned before the first entry, or null.
